*外側旋轉步 (Outside Spin) 
*外側換步 (Outside Change) 
*帚形步 (Whisk) 
*退帚形步 (Back Whisk) 
*退鎖步 (Backward Lock) 
*並退帚形步 (Fallaway Whisk)                   
*分式滑雪形轉步 (Open Telemark)            
